NEW YORK! Tomorrow is the last day to register to vote, this is something you can do online, so you literally have ZERO excuses.


Check to see if you're registered [here](https://voterlookup.elections.state.ny.us/).


If you're not, register [here](https://dmv.ny.gov/more-info/electronic-voter-registration-application).


You may hate the two candidates running for POTUS, but they are not the only ones up for election this year.


Find out who's on your ballot [here](http://whosontheballot.org/).